# Agent Instructions Template

This directory should contain agent-specific instruction files.

## Recommended Files

### research-agent.md
Instructions for research agents working on this item.

### design-agent.md
Instructions for design agents working on this item.

### implementation-agent.md
Instructions for implementation agents working on this item.

### testing-agent.md
Instructions for testing agents working on this item.

## Template for Agent Instructions

```markdown
# [Agent Type] Agent Instructions

**For:** [Agent Type] Agent working on [Item Title]
**Item ID:** YYYY-MM-DD-[slug]
**Current Stage:** [current stage]

---

## Your Mission

[Brief description of what this agent should accomplish]

---

## Key Tasks

1. [Task 1]
2. [Task 2]
3. [Task 3]

---

## Deliverables

- [Deliverable 1]
- [Deliverable 2]

---

## Success Criteria

- [ ] [Criterion 1]
- [ ] [Criterion 2]

---

## Notes

[Any additional context or guidance]

---

**Last Updated:** YYYY-MM-DD
```
